  "prompt": "How to get more RP (free) than 400 in LoL?",
  "response": "In **League of Legends**, RP (**Riot Points**) is the premium currency used to purchase skins, champions, and other cosmetic items. Unfortunately, Riot Games does not offer a direct way to earn RP for free beyond certain limited-time events or promotions. However, there are a few ways to maximize your chances of obtaining RP or content that usually costs RP without spending money:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Participate in Official Riot Events**\n   - Riot occasionally gives away free RP or skin rewards during special events, such as **Worlds**, **anniversaries**, or **milestone celebrations**.\n   - Keep an eye on the **client news** and **official social media** for announcements.\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Earn Hextech Chests and Keys**\n   - By playing well and earning **S grades** on champions, you can unlock **Hextech Chests**. These chests can contain **champion shards**, **skin shards**, or **key fragments**.\n   - Combine key fragments to open chests and hope for **skin shards**, which can be unlocked without RP if you have enough **Blue Essence** or **Orange Essence**.\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Use the Prime Gaming Capsules**\n   - If you have an **Amazon Prime membership**, you can link your Riot account to Prime Gaming and receive free monthly rewards, including **LoL capsules** that may contain RP, skins, or other in-game content.\n   - This is technically \"free\" if you already have a Prime membership.\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Win Giveaways or Contests**\n   - Follow **Riot Games** and **League of Legends influencers** on platforms like Twitter, Reddit, or YouTube. They often host giveaways where you can win RP, skins, or other rewards.\n   - Be cautious of scams and only participate in official or verified contests.\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Play on PBE (Public Beta Environment)**\n   - While this doesn\u2019t directly give you RP, you can test out skins and champions for free on the **PBE server**.\n   - This is a great way to enjoy content that usually costs RP without spending money.\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Complete Missions and Events**\n   - Some events and missions reward **Orange Essence**, which can be used to unlock skin shards without spending RP.\n   - Additionally, events like **Mythic Essence shops** often allow you to purchase rare skins with earned currency.\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Refer-a-Friend Program**\n   - While this program is no longer active in most regions, it used to reward players with RP for referring friends who reached certain milestones. Keep an eye out if it ever returns.\n\n---\n\n### Important Notes:\n- RP is primarily a premium currency, and Riot Games encourages players to purchase it directly.\n- Be wary of **third-party websites** or scams claiming to offer free RP. These are often fraudulent and can result in your account being compromised or banned.\n\n---\n\nBy participating in events, playing regularly, and taking advantage of free rewards, you can unlock content that would otherwise require RP. However, earning more than 400 RP for free is very unlikely without spending money or participating in specific promotions.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
